<paragraph id="3739B4945C8C85CFAF6D78ED41EF60DF" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">
<taxonomicName id="B893FE59C8745B5704E805E56EEC13D6" authority="Mayr, 1861" authorityName="Mayr" authorityYear="1861" baseAuthorityName="Forel" baseAuthorityYear="1911" class="Insecta" family="Formicidae" genus="Temnothorax" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Temnothorax graecus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="species" species="graecus">
<emphasis id="26E21361C17AE8BA53836CBE4A8BC665" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658">Temnothorax graecus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has a range restricted to Greece, the Republic of North Macedonia and Bulgaria. Prior to this study, there was only one record of this species from Bulgaria (Central Stara Planina Mts: Gabrovo) (
<bibRefCitation id="95506AA57C232C22C18CE0CD48EC863D" author="Lapeva-Gjonova, A." journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="83658" pagination="1 - 124" refId="B7725831" refString="Lapeva-Gjonova, A., Antonova, V., Radchenko, A. G., Atanasova, M., 2010. Catalogue of the ants (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) of Bulgaria. ZooKeys 62: 1 - 124" title="Catalogue of the ants (Hymenoptera: Formicidae) of Bulgaria" volume="62" year="2010">Lapeva-Gjonova et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
